msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:25
msgid "**EU CELLAR**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:25
msgid "European Union legislation (Formex v4)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:25
msgid "`CFMX4…`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:25
msgid "**Operaton DMN 1.3**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:25
msgid "Deployed DMN decision models (experimental)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:25
msgid "`DMN1.3_…`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:32
msgid ""
"For BWB and CVDR, \"latest version valid on a given date\" queries are "
"resolved automatically through SRU search of the repository, so callers do "
"not need to know the exact publication index."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:36
msgid "Rule path navigation"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:38
msgid ""
"Rules within a publication are hierarchically structured (hoofdstuk → "
"paragraaf → artikel → lid → onderdeel). The `/rules/{rule_id_path}` endpoint "
"accepts a comma-separated path of identifiers to navigate directly to any "
"level:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:40
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api\\features\\overview.md:40"
msgid "BWBR0015703_2025-07-01_0, Artikel 20, lid 1, onderdeel a."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:44
msgid ""
"The path traversal is **depth-first** and **alphanumeric-only** (all non-"
"alphanumeric characters including whitespace are stripped before matching), "
"so `\"onderdeel a.\"` and `\"onderdeel a\"` resolve identically. "
"Intermediate identifiers can be omitted when there is no ambiguity."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:48
msgid "Multiple output formats"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:50
msgid ""
"Every response can be serialised in seven formats via the `format` query "
"parameter:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:52
msgid "Format"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:52
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api\\features\\overview.md:52"
msgid "Description"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:52
msgid "`cprmv-json` *(default)*"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:52
msgid "Custom JSON with recursive rule tree — human-readable"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:52
