#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:52
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api\\features\\overview.md:52"
msgid "`n3`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:52
msgid "N3 RDF serialisation"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:52
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api\\features\\overview.md:52"
msgid "`xml`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:52
msgid "RDF/XML serialisation"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:61
msgid ""
"The `cprmv-json` format produces a nested dictionary representation of the "
"rule and all its contained sub-rules, with predicate URIs as keys — designed "
"for readability and direct use in downstream processing."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:65
msgid "Definition extraction with `unformat`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:67
msgid ""
"The `unformat` query parameter accepts a [`parse`]{1} pattern string to "
"extract structured values from a rule's `cprmv:definition` literal. When "
"supplied, the format is forced to `cprmv-json` and the parsed named fields "
"are merged into the response alongside the full rule data:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:69
msgid "unformat={situatie:param_value}: € {norm:param_value}"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:73
msgid ""
"This enables structured extraction of domain values (e.g. income limits, "
"thresholds) directly from natural-language rule definitions without "
"additional post-processing."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:77
msgid "Reference resolution"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:79
msgid ""
"The `/ref/{referencemethod}/{reference}` endpoint accepts external legal "
"reference URIs and redirects to the corresponding CPRMV API path:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:81
msgid ""
"**Juriconnect** (`jci1.3` and `jci1.31`) — maps BWB identifiers and locatie-"
"strings to `/rules/` paths. Supported locatie types: `artikel`, `hoofdstuk`, "
"`paragraaf`, `onderdeel`, `lid`. Sighting date is accepted in the URI but "
"ignored (defaults to today)."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:82
