#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Creference-resolution.md:1
msgid "Reference Resolution"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Creference-resolution.md:3
msgid ""
"The `/ref/{referencemethod}/{reference}` endpoint accepts external legal "
"reference URIs and resolves them to a CPRMV API `/rules/` path, returning an "
"HTTP redirect."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Creference-resolution.md:5
msgid ""
"This allows other systems that produce Juriconnect or ELI references to pass "
"them directly to the CPRMV API without needing to understand the internal ID "
"format."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Creference-resolution.md:9
msgid "Juriconnect"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Creference-resolution.md:11
msgid ""
"Both `jci1.3` and `jci1.31` versions are supported. The `referencemethod` "
"path segment should be `Juriconnect` (case-insensitive handling is not "
"guaranteed — use as shown)."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Creference-resolution.md:13
msgid ""
"**Supported locatie types:** `artikel`, `hoofdstuk`, `paragraaf`, "
"`onderdeel`, `lid`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Creference-resolution.md:15
msgid "**Example reference:**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Creference-resolution.md:17
msgid ""
"jci1.3:c:BWBR0015703&hoofdstuk=3&paragraaf=3.2&artikel=20&z=2025-07-"
"01&g=2025-07-01"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Creference-resolution.md:21
msgid ""
"The `z` (gezien-op / sighting date) parameter is accepted but currently "
"ignored. The `g` (geldig-op / valid-on date) parameter is used to resolve "
"the correct publication version."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Creference-resolution.md:23
msgid "The API constructs a redirect to:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Creference-resolution.md:25
msgid ""
"/rules/BWBR0015703_{date}_latest/"
"hoofdstuk%203%2Cparagraaf%203.2%2CArtikel%2020"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Creference-resolution.md:29
msgid "**Limitations:**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Creference-resolution.md:31
msgid ""
"Only single-consolidation references are supported; multi-consolidation "
"(`mconsolidatie`) is not."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Creference-resolution.md:32
msgid ""
"The full set of locatie types supported by the Juriconnect standard may not "
"all be implemented in the BWB XSLT transform."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Creference-resolution.md:33
msgid "BWB ID must be exactly 8 characters (`BWBRxxxxxxx`)."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Creference-resolution.md:37
msgid "ELI"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Creference-resolution.md:39
msgid ""
"The ELI reference method is registered in the methods KG "
"(`cprmvmethods:referencemethods`) but the transform function "
"(`transform_eli_reference`) returns `None` — not yet implemented."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Creference-resolution.md:43
msgid "Reference method configuration"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Creference-resolution.md:45
msgid ""
"The supported reference methods and their parameter mappings are defined in "
"`data/cprmvmethods.ttl` under the `cprmvmethods:referencemethods` RDF list. "
"Each method entry carries:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Creference-resolution.md:47
msgid ""
"`cprmv-serve:reference-mapping-valid-on` — the query parameter name that "
"carries the valid-on date in the external reference format."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Creference-resolution.md:48
msgid ""
"`cprmv-serve:reference-mapping-seen-on` — the query parameter name for the "
"sighting date."
msgstr ""

