#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cuser-guide%5Cfetching-rules.md:100
msgid "Extracting structured values with unformat"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cuser-guide%5Cfetching-rules.md:102
msgid ""
"When a rule definition contains a parseable pattern, `unformat` extracts "
